<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Tournament Management Account Credentials</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f8fafc; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: white; }
    .header { background-color: #10b981; color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; text-align: center; }
    .content { padding: 30px; }
    .credentials-box { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 25px; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 20px 0; }
    .credentials-title { color: #1e40af; margin-top: 0; text-align: center; }
    .credential-item { margin: 8px 0; font-size: 16px; }
    .credential-label { font-weight: bold; }
    .credential-value { font-family: monospace; background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 3px; }
    .password-value { background-color: #fef3c7; color: #92400e; }
    .role-badge { background-color: #ecfdf5; color: #065f46; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: bold; }
    .login-button { display: inline-block; background-color: #10b981; color: white; padding: 14px 28px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: bold; margin: 20px 0; box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2); }
    .warning-box { background-color: #fef3c7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; }
    .info-box { background-color: #ecfdf5; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #10b981; }
    .footer { background-color: #f8fafc; padding: 20px; text-align: center; color: #6b7280; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer h4 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #374151; }
    ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; }
    li { margin: 5px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">üéØ Your Account Has Been Created</h1>
      <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Welcome to the Tournament Management System</p>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="credentials-box">
        <h2 class="credentials-title">Your Login Credentials</h2>

        <div style="background-color: #f0f9ff; padding: 15px; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #0ea5e9;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #0c4a6e;">üìã Account Details</h3>
          <p class="credential-item">
            <span class="credential-label">Username:</span>
            <span class="credential-value">{{username}}</span>
          </p>
          <p class="credential-item">
            <span class="credential-label">Password:</span>
            <span class="credential-value password-value">{{password}}</span>
          </p>
          <p class="credential-item">
            <span class="credential-label">Role:</span>
            <span class="role-badge">{{role}}</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="login-button">üîê Login to Your Account</a>
      </div>

      <div class="warning-box">
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #92400e;">‚ö†Ô∏è Important Security Notice</h4>
        <ul style="color: #92400e;">
          <li>Keep your credentials secure and do not share them</li>
          <li>Change your password after first login for better security</li>
          <li>Contact your administrator if you have any issues</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="info-box">
        <h4 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #065f46;">üéØ Getting Started</h4>
        <ol style="color: #065f46;">
          <li>Click the login button above</li>
          <li>Use your username and password to sign in</li>
          <li>Explore your role-specific features</li>
          <li>Consider updating your password for security</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <p style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0; color: #6b7280;">
        If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact your system administrator.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <strong>Tournament Management System</strong><br>
      Best regards, Tournament Management Team
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
